comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T18:06:39.089Z",codex-derived-context-20260721,"Duplicate check: searched all statuses for quota-limited review required branch protection, Greptile Review branch protection, and unavailable quota required checks. Existing pm-92if owns quality policy and historical pm-bkcv/pm-0fxa own earlier Greptile/review tooling, but no active item owns fail-open branch protection when a paid/free review quota is exhausted; this is the canonical policy item."
  "2026-07-21T18:09:44.027Z",codex-derived-context-20260721,"Live GitHub evidence 2026-07-21: Greptile CLI returned free_reviews_limit_reached; main branch protection required Greptile Review despite no status context, blocking otherwise-green PR #633. Removed only Greptile Review via the required-status-context API. The 18 deterministic requirements remain strict: build foundation, three runtime smokes, coverage/typecheck/static/compat/smoke gates, Windows regression, docs, CodeQL analysis, Trivy, ShellCheck, PSScriptAnalyzer, actionlint, Codecov patch, and CodeFactor. CodeRabbit/Gemini/Sourcery were already advisory."
  "2026-07-21T21:36:59.151Z",codex-relationship-backfill-20260721,"Current-head evidence 2026-07-21: committed SDK backfill bundle 3b8ae4b7 passed all deterministic release stages, including exact 100/100/100/100 coverage, secret scan, packed npx smoke, and 88-command package-first dogfood. The final advisory Greptile CLI stage alone returned free_reviews_limit_reached. PR bot triggers will still be attempted and documented; quota failure must not weaken deterministic required checks or be misreported as a code failure."
  "2026-07-22T18:05:28.536Z",codex-root,"PR #644 exact-head evidence 2026-07-22: every deterministic repository-owned release gate passed, including 6,084 tests at exact 100/100/100/100, 100% docstrings, static quality, package boundary, token budget, secrets, packed npm smoke, and 88-command package-first dogfood. The final advisory Greptile CLI stage alone returned free_reviews_limit_reached after warning that uncommitted review-fix files were outside its review. Hosted @greptileai was also triggered on the PR and produced no review surface. This is external quota state, not a code failure."
body: ""
